<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.9">
<l>tuvarik kaṉivāy nilamaṅkai tuyartīrn tuyyap pāratattuḷ</l>
<l>ivarit taracar taṭumāṟa viruḷnāḷ piṟanta vammāṉai</l>
<l>yuvari yōtam muttunta vorupā lorupā loṇcennel</l>
<l>kavari vīcuṅ kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who was born at nighttime so that the lady earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">with coral[-colored] fruit lips, was saved, [her] sorrows ending,</l>
<l>[And] so that kings were disarrayed, opposing [them]</l>
<l rend="indent">in the Bhārata [War],</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Kaṇṇapuram</l>
<l rend="indent">where bright red paddy waves like a whisk</l>
<l>On one side, as on the other side, the salty sea waves cast up pearls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
